meta.summary: Week/Year based on US Weeks (Sun-Sat). By default, if a week spans multiple years or quarters (ie, end of the year/quarter), it is marked as first or last week of the period according to particular standards (ie, US or EU). Labels marked as "Continuous" show both weeks (W53/2009 - W1/2010).
